snippet.title: Keep Those Bugs Away From The Bomb - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the reveal trailer of Keep Those Bugs Away From The Bomb! 

Survive the swarm and clear the arena of alien infestation in this fast-paced bullet hell roguelite shooter. Unlock new heroes, guns, and skills in endless campaigns designed for quick runs and high replayability. Your objective is simple: Keep Those Bugs Away From The Bomb!
Wishlist the game on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2133500/Keep_Those_Bugs_Away_From_the_Bomb/
